wmjulia is a captivating graphical utility that generates and displays
an animated Julia set, a fascinating fractal image derived from
complex numbers. Designed primarily as a dock or wharf applet for
Window Maker and Afterstep desktop environments, wmjulia provides
a dynamic and visually engaging element for your desktop. It continuously
renders and animates the intricate patterns of the Julia set, offering
a unique blend of mathematical beauty and aesthetic appeal. This
applet serves as both a decorative addition and a subtle demonstration
of fractal geometry, enhancing the visual experience for users
of compatible window managers.
